#: resources/views/help/data-fixes.phtml
msgid "For example, we can quickly find individuals that do not have a death event, but it is much slower to calculate if the individual is dead."
msgstr "Na primjer, možemo brzo pronaći osobe koje nemaju smrtni slučaj, ali mnogo je sporije izračunati je li ta osoba mrtva."

